=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:29,900
=Episode 26=

19
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,800
I got it.

20
00:01:37,190 --> 00:01:38,160
Dou Qi Continent

21
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,080
respects powerhouses the most.

22
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:44,440
Many people are misled by the lust for power.

23
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:47,760
The Hall of Souls is the worst result.

24
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,000
In that case,

25
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,830
Xiao Xuan used his power properly

26
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,360
to seal Huntian Emperor.

27
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,670
Senior,

28
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,510
do you have any unfulfilled wishes?

29
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,440
I'll help you meet them when I go out.

30
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,720
You try this hard to flatter me.

31
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,910
Do you want my treasures as well?

32
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,390
Although I don't know about them,

33
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,470
the treasures

34
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,630
must not be seized by the Hall of Souls.

35
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:32,390
Your tone sounds exactly the same as his.

36
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,230
Fine.

37
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,600
You can have

38
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,160
all the stuff

39
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:39,360
as my goodbye

40
00:02:39,830 --> 00:02:41,080
to the past

41
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,290
between Xiao Xuan and me.

42
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:48,230
Senior,

43
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,600
what's the treasure on earth?

44
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,910
Near the sky, alone and high I stand.

45
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:57,440
In my tea house, no one is present.

46
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:01,160
Envy, greed, wrath and lust.

47
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:05,800
Illusion is the ultimate world.

48
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,520
Where's that old man?

49
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:16,160
Is the treasure he mentions

50
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:17,670
these bones?

51
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:22,750
Your Highness, be careful!

52
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,200
Go.

53
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,600
(His weakness is the mask.)

54
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,040
(Three Thousand Thunder Movement.)

55
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:45,270
Fire-splitting Wave-gnawing Ruler!

56
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,040
Xiao Yan.

57
00:05:21,550 --> 00:05:24,160
It looks like I have to do it myself.

58
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:31,510
Mine. Mine. Mine.

59
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,760
All mine.

60
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:33,880
All mine.

61
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,070
- They're all mine.
- Dad?

62
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:37,040
Mine. Mine. All mine.

63
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,110
These are all mine.

64
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:39,070
These are all mine.

65
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,040
These are all mine.

66
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,640
All mine.

67
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:42,630
Dad?

68
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:45,790
Dad!

69
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:49,630
Dad.

70
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,560
Nightmare?

71
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,880
Xiao Yan,

72
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:26,670
do you think

73
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,760
my father is greedy?

74
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,640
Do you think he's the same as Hall of Souls

75
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,720
who covet Dou Saint's treasure?

76
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:36,670
Does he…

77
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:39,550
deserve to die?

78
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:43,000
Why is your innocent mind

79
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,830
bothered by complicated questions?

80
00:06:47,670 --> 00:06:48,510
Do you know

81
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:50,670
why Dou Saint gave the bones to me,

82
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,440
not the Hall of Souls?

83
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,720
Power is neutral in nature.

84
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:00,110
Its quality depends on how you use it.

85
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,830
Your father went after power

86
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,480
to save his clansmen.

87
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,830
He didn't hurt others.

88
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,670
He was totally different

89
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,950
from the Hall of Souls.

90
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:15,320
Why did Dou Saint ask me not to be obsessed?

91
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:19,760
Personally,

92
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,510
I'm obsessed with saving Mr. Yao,

93
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,600
with fighting against the Hall of Souls,

94
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:27,600
with protecting Xun'er,

95
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,480
and with protecting you guys.

96
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,350
I'm just one of the common people.

97
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:38,040
I can let it go

98
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,790
only if I finish all my desires.

99
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,480
I don't quite understand what you said,

100
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,760
but I think it makes sense.

101
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,480
Here you are.

102
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,160
This's the treasure your father searched for.

103
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:12,600
Why do you give it to me?

104
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,720
You will go back to Dragon Tribe soon.

105
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:18,110
It might help you.

106
00:08:23,110 --> 00:08:24,110
I've thought it through.

107
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:26,510
I'm going to protect my clansmen

108
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,720
in my own way.

109
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,910
I'll return to Dragon Island
with Grandpa Hei Qing tomorrow.

110
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:39,310
Wind Sage,

111
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:41,550
this is what the Dou Saint gave me.

112
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,910
Elders of Hall of Souls kept fighting with me

113
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:46,280
to get these bones.

114
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,940
After the fight with the Hall of Souls,

115
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,080
I have been thinking

116
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,230
that its plot

117
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,520
must involve more people than Mu Gu.

118
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,760
You were attacked
by an Elder of Hall of Souls now.

119
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,320
The picture unfolds more clearly.

120
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:13,840
Is there a mastermind behind Mu Gu?

121
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:16,080
It must be Hun Miesheng.

122
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:20,670
Elders of Hall of Souls raised
a big commotion,

123
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,390
so, the bones

124
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:25,000
must be connected to their next step.

125
00:09:26,470 --> 00:09:27,910
I've studied the bones all the way here,

126
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,520
but I didn't discover any secrets.

127
00:09:34,230 --> 00:09:36,000
That Dou Saint gave you the bones

128
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,440
because you are a descendant of Xiao Clan.

129
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:40,280
The puzzle must be solved
with your unique method.

130
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,950
Senior Xiao Xuan was excelled
at Heavenly Flames.

131
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,790
Try to burn them with your Heavenly Flames.

132
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,040
OK.

133
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,440
Two moons come together.

134
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:04,670
Nine planets line up.

135
00:10:06,590 --> 00:10:08,000
Tides flood the world.

136
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,350
The demon flame surfaces.

137
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,050
It refers to Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

138
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:15,000
It's the third on Heavenly Flames Ranking

139
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,350
with a forbidding power.

140
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:19,080
The next target of the Hall of Souls

141
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:20,590
is Purifying Lotus Demon Flame!

142
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:23,510
Keep burning.

143
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:36,430
This is…

144
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,830
The incomplete map of the Heavenly Flames.

145
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:40,920
This is why

146
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,440
Dou Saint gave the bones to you.

147
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,110
As this is the case,

148
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:47,790
the Hall of Souls won't simply give up

149
00:10:48,230 --> 00:10:50,760
since they failed at the relic of Dou Saint.

150
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,880
They will come to the Starfall Hall.

151
00:10:54,350 --> 00:10:55,520
There's not much time for you.

152
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,890
You must refine the Soul Infant Fruit ASAP

153
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,920
and wake Yao Chen up.

154
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:17,720
Did Yao Chen

155
00:11:18,230 --> 00:11:19,710
tell you about this cauldron?

156
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,670
It's called Black Demon Cauldron.

157
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,880
Yao Chen found it in the relic of a Dou Saint

158
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,200
when he traveled across the Central Plains.

159
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,030
After years of use,

160
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,960
it had developed a sturdy body.

161
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,110
Though without poles or cracks,

162
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,590
it had absorbed flame energy

163
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:42,970
and become the best medicinal cauldron.

164
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,040
Black Iron?

165
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:53,230
Not wanting to waste such a treasure,

166
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:54,840
Yao Chen took it back

167
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,470
and stored it in the Starfall Hall.

168
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:57,750
It's seldom shown.

169
00:11:59,000 --> 00:11:59,840
If not for

170
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:01,550
the refinery of Soul Infant Fruit,

171
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,960
which requires three of your Heavenly Flames,

172
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,320
I won't take it out.

173
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,400
Three flames?

174
00:12:10,550 --> 00:12:12,470
It's difficult enough for ordinary cauldrons

175
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:13,310
to bear two flames.

176
00:12:13,710 --> 00:12:14,710
As for three flames,

177
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,880
only Black Demon Cauldron can do it.

178
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:20,320
Wield all your Flame Mantra and Qi Methods

179
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:21,510
that you've learnt.

180
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:23,030
Gather the flame power

181
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,280
into this Black Demon Cauldron.

182
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,400
This way, Soul Infant Fruit can be refined.

183
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,840
My life

184
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,640
was saved by Mr. Yao in Misty Cloud Mountain.

185
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,910
I'll do everything I can and try my best

186
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,760
to help my teacher recover his power.

187
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:39,210
Focus on refining the medicine.

188
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,880
Even if havoc comes,

189
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,550
I'll defend the Hall with Qingluan.

190
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,120
Don't be distracted.

191
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,480
I won't.

192
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:52,520
(Channel your Dou Qi into the cauldron slowly.)

193
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,280
(Trigger Flame Mantra.)

194
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:21,870
(Now,)

195
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,030
(put Soul Infant Fruit)

196
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,910
(inside the cauldron.)

197
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:27,280
(After it absorbs Dou Qi,)

198
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:30,400
(warm it with the less-scorching flame.)

199
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,840
(When its property is displayed a bit,)

200
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,710
(add the second flame.)

201
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:37,350
(Deepen the extent little by little,)

202
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,230
(until the refinery is finished.)

203
00:14:31,110 --> 00:14:33,000
He's been inside for two days and nights.

204
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:35,710
Can he make it out today?

205
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,000
No news

206
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,760
is good news.

207
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:42,750
Master.

208
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,210
- Si Zhu, what's wrong?
- Master.

209
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:46,280
There's…There's someone…

210
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:47,470
Master, there's someone outside.

211
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,360
Master,

212
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,840
the Sky Bell keeps ringing.

213
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,200
It's an unkind visit!

214
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:02,960
Like it or not,
there's no escaping the inevitable.

215
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:08,860
(Starfall Hall)

216
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:11,230
Qingluan, lead everyone to Dou Technique Hall.

217
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:12,510
Hurry up.

218
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:15,000
Master, they juniors should retreat.

219
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,670
I want to fight enemies with you.

220
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:18,200
Senior, we're not leaving as well.

221
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:19,630
Go!

222
00:15:21,350 --> 00:15:22,190
Yes.

223
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:29,420
(Starfall Hall)

224
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,320
Be polite when you visit us.

225
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:36,510
Now that you're there,

226
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:39,030
stop sneaking around!

227
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:45,720
Hun Miesheng,

228
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,280
I knew you didn't die.

229
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,280
Leave now.

230
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,600
Hurry!

231
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,670
Are you here for your broken bones,

232
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:39,200
or your lost soul?

233
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,840
50 years ago,

234
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:44,030
if not for the intervention of Gu Clan,

235
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,320
you guys should have been buried

236
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:49,200
deep under the Starfall Hall.

237
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,230
Stop putting on an act!

238
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:54,000
Let me see

239
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,710
what you are.

240
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,350
Exhaust all your strength and skills.

241
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:05,720
I'd like to see

242
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:08,430
if you're still able to kill me.

243
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,800
You do get older.

244
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,280
Taiyi Gale!

245
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:11,760
(Focus on refining the medicine.)

246
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,110
(Even if havoc comes,)

247
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,280
(I'll defend the Hall with Qingluan.)

248
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:38,110
Shing stars and four Gods.

249
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:41,230
Eight Taoist Trigrams.

250
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,350
Qiankun Protection!

251
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,000
Brother Mu!

252
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,000
Si Zhu.

253
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,600
Brother Mu!

254
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,520
Little Fairy Doctor,

255
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:44,910
protect…

256
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:46,310
protect Dou Technique Hall.

257
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,360
We fight

258
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:50,720
for the Hall.

259
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:57,030
(Wind Sage.)

260
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:58,190
(Little Fairy Doctor.)

261
00:19:58,800 --> 00:19:59,640
(Brother Mu.)

262
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:01,710
(Please hold on.)

263
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,400
Mr. Yao.

264
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,240
Xiao Yan.

265
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:04,590
Their Dou Qi is condensed on their masks.

266
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:06,590
Smash their masks,

267
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:07,800
and they will disappear.

268
00:21:09,190 --> 00:21:10,520
Fire-splitting Wave-gnawing Ruler!

269
00:21:21,640 --> 00:21:22,480
Are you OK?

270
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:24,160
Wind Sage is in the bamboo grove.

271
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:52,880
Can you feel it?

272
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:55,950
It's the power of a Demi Dou Saint.

273
00:21:57,710 --> 00:22:00,350
You were sealed in the Bodhisattva Tree
by the Gu Clan.

274
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,800
How could you surpass the Dou Venerate level?

275
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,640
The old Hun Miesheng did die

276
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:14,190
50 years ago.

277
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:17,000
The current version of me

278
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:21,310
has the power you can never dream of.

279
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:24,950
Feng Xian,

280
00:22:26,950 --> 00:22:29,680
you should feel lucky to be killed

281
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:31,880
by a stronger man.

282
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:36,760
